  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网执行器控制器（ActuatorController）的固件版本管理画一个Git流程图。主分支要有四个关键提交点，标记为a、b、c、d，代表从初始化到量产的完整生命周期。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit a",
        "commit b",
        "commit c",
        "commit d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，主分支四个提交a→b→c→d。那并行开发的部分呢？通常工业控制器会有多团队并行开发功能模块，需要几条特性分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch1",
        "branch2",
        "branch3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要三条特性分支。branch1做紧急补丁，从初始提交a分出来；branch2做传感器校准优化，也从a开始；branch3做通信协议升级，这个要晚一点从主分支创建，等b提交之后再分出来，因为协议升级依赖b里的基础接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch1",
        "branch2",
        "branch3",
        "commit a",
        "commit b"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下分支顺序：branch1和branch2都从a创建，branch3从b之后创建。那三条分支的显示顺序怎么排？branch1最左，branch3最右？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch1 order: 0",
        "branch2 order: 1",
        "branch3 order: 3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，branch1放最左边，branch2中间，branch3最右边。branch1上有个关键提交j，是紧急修复电机过流保护；branch2上提交x是校准算法；branch3上提交u是协议握手优化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch1",
        "commit j",
        "branch2",
        "commit x",
        "branch3",
        "commit u"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，主分支和三条特性分支都建好了，各自的提交也标记完成。接下来处理合并流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "branch1",
        "branch2",
        "branch3",
        "commit j",
        "commit x",
        "commit u"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "合并策略要体现工业控制的严谨性。branch3的协议升级最复杂，先在c提交之后把main合并进branch3做集成验证；验证通过后，主分支继续走到d量产版本。然后branch1和branch2分别合并main，确保所有特性都基于最终量产版本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch3",
        "merge main",
        "main",
        "commit c",
        "commit d",
        "branch1",
        "branch2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全理解：先反向合并main→branch3做预集成，然后主分支推进到d，最后两个正向合并branch1→main和branch2→main。这样所有特性分支都收敛到量产版本d，符合工业固件发布的流程要求。",
      "elements_involved": [
